<p class="slds-m-bottom--large">
  Made with <a href="http://emberjs.com/">Ember</a>, <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/">Rails</a>, the <a href="www.lightningdesignsystem.com">Salesforce Lightning Design System</a>, and love by the
